attributes.Long form description: The student is preparing to play their Nintendo Switch with a friend. They attach the Joy-Con controllers to straps, so they can hold them more easily. They put the Switch in its kickstand and exchange games and micro SD cards with their friend. They turn on the Switch and begin playing.
